  <summary date="2021-05-12T18:33:25Z" status="Introduced in House">Protecting Local Authority and Neighborhoods Act or the PLAN Act

This bill addresses the current protection from liability enjoyed by interactive computer services (e.g., social media companies) for content posted on their sites by third parties. Specifically, it provides that this protection does not extend to certain claims that a service knowingly facilitated illegal leases or rentals of real property.</summary>
